  <description><![CDATA[<p class="p1">Overlooking the lake and valley, the Hotel Ariston is a family-run hotel offering comfortable rooms and easy access to the lake. In a peaceful location, this hotel is great for exploring all that <a data-udi="umb://document/6d3c5ed21e9544a292fe722aa587aa10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d3c5ed21e9544a292fe722aa587aa10}" title="Lake Levico">Lake Levico</a> has to offer. Decorated in traditional style, this hotel combines friendly service with great cuisine in a convivial atmosphere. The outdoor pool with whirlpool and surrounding sun terrace are a particular highlight. The Ariston is the closest hotel in our programme to the lake which lies just 50m away. Ariston guests may also use the facilities of the sister establishment <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6ad11a69794f8fa86a029f330148a3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6ad11a69794f8fa86a029f330148a3}" title="Hotel Ambassador">Hotel Ambassador</a> (pay locally).</p>
<p class="p1">At Hotel Ariston, a Val Sugana resort card is included in your stay and can be collected from your hotel. Please note the Val Sugana card is in use from 13 May 19 until the end of seaons, subject to tourist board changes.</p>]]></description>
